00:00:56.890 --> 00:00:59.530 align:middle line:84%
to do with beauty products
now, the word alchemy

00:00:59.530 --> 00:01:00.830 align:middle line:90%
is all over the place.

00:01:00.830 --> 00:01:03.870 align:middle line:84%
