00:01:04.967 --> 00:01:06.800 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVEN ROSS: I would
say that's very fair.

00:01:06.800 --> 00:01:10.100 align:middle line:10%
And it really leads
us into a subject

00:01:10.100 --> 00:01:12.420 align:middle line:10%
that I think is
very, very important.

00:01:12.420 --> 00:01:18.030 align:middle line:10%
And that is when you look at
terminology from ancient times,

00:01:18.030 --> 00:01:20.310 align:middle line:10%
from past
civilizations, and they

00:01:20.310 --> 00:01:25.180 align:middle line:10%
use words that are relatively
close to the words we use,

00:01:25.180 --> 00:01:28.310 align:middle line:10%
the difference really
is astronomical.

00:01:28.310 --> 00:01:32.070 align:middle line:10%
As an example, in ancient
times, the word magic

00:01:32.070 --> 00:01:36.740 align:middle line:10%
meant one who understood
the workings of nature.

00:01:36.740 --> 00:01:40.560 align:middle line:84%
Now, magic has that
connotation of being-- it

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:44.570 align:middle line:84%
could be black magic, it could
be very, very mysterious.

00:01:44.570 --> 00:01:50.640 align:middle line:84%
But the magi, the magician,
was very highly thought of,

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:53.010 align:middle line:90%
because they understood.

00:01:53.010 --> 00:01:56.830 align:middle line:84%
We will get into
another term that really

00:01:56.830 --> 00:01:58.360 align:middle line:84%
is associated with
the alchemists,

00:01:58.360 --> 00:02:00.620 align:middle line:84%
and that is the
word imagination.

00:02:00.620 --> 00:02:01.559 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Oh, yes.

00:02:01.559 --> 00:02:03.600 align:middle line:84%
We're going to spend a
little time in that realm.

00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:06.660 align:middle line:84%
Because that's very different
in today's parlance as well.

00:02:06.660 --> 00:02:08.210 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Definitely.

00:02:08.210 --> 00:02:11.450 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Going back
to the term alchemy,

00:02:11.450 --> 00:02:14.800 align:middle line:84%
back in the day, when people
used their language very

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:18.270 align:middle line:84%
carefully and had a completely
different understanding of it

00:02:18.270 --> 00:02:21.590 align:middle line:84%
than an chemical
marriage between

00:02:21.590 --> 00:02:23.950 align:middle line:84%
say, two elements to
make a finer beauty

00:02:23.950 --> 00:02:25.525 align:middle line:90%
product, for example.

00:02:25.525 --> 00:02:29.170 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:02:29.170 --> 00:02:32.050 align:middle line:84%
Let's talk about what their
lifestyle was at the time.

00:02:32.050 --> 00:02:36.640 align:middle line:84%
Because as you've told me off
camera, this was a lifestyle.

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:40.020 align:middle line:84%
Alchemy was an actual way
of living for these men.

00:02:40.020 --> 00:02:41.470 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: That is very true.

00:02:41.470 --> 00:02:47.020 align:middle line:84%
Now, also in alchemy, I
include the term theurgy,

00:02:47.020 --> 00:02:49.940 align:middle line:84%
which was a practice
of the ancient Greeks.

00:02:49.940 --> 00:02:53.550 align:middle line:84%
Because alchemy is
looking for a change

00:02:53.550 --> 00:02:55.910 align:middle line:90%
of state, a transformation.

00:02:55.910 --> 00:02:58.200 align:middle line:10%
So when we talk
about alchemy, I want

00:02:58.200 --> 00:03:03.100 align:middle line:10%
to include a couple of other
regimens that are so close.

00:03:03.100 --> 00:03:08.150 align:middle line:10%
What the ancients were trying
to do through the term alchemy

00:03:08.150 --> 00:03:14.750 align:middle line:10%
was to blend opposites
to achieve a oneness.

00:03:14.750 --> 00:03:17.680 align:middle line:90%
And that sounds very simplistic.

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:24.360 align:middle line:84%
And it is simplistic, because
they said alchemy was using art

00:03:24.360 --> 00:03:26.510 align:middle line:90%
to perfect nature.

00:03:26.510 --> 00:03:30.750 align:middle line:84%
It is speeding up
a natural process

00:03:30.750 --> 00:03:34.310 align:middle line:84%
through the use of
the art, alchemy,

00:03:34.310 --> 00:03:36.700 align:middle line:90%
to achieve a something.

00:03:36.700 --> 00:03:41.210 align:middle line:84%
Now, you and I spoke
recently, again, off camera,

00:03:41.210 --> 00:03:45.070 align:middle line:84%
leading to this show, that
we live in a fast food era.

00:03:45.070 --> 00:03:47.450 align:middle line:84%
And the word alchemy
now really means

00:03:47.450 --> 00:03:54.040 align:middle line:84%
somebody is going to find the
magic elixir, that magic rod,

00:03:54.040 --> 00:03:56.830 align:middle line:84%
the Philosopher's
Stone, and they

00:03:56.830 --> 00:04:01.290 align:middle line:84%
are going to have all knowledge,
all wisdom, all abilities

00:04:01.290 --> 00:04:02.520 align:middle line:90%
to do everything.

00:04:02.520 --> 00:04:05.050 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That's a modern day
word of use of the word magic,

00:04:05.050 --> 00:04:05.550 align:middle line:90%
by the way.

00:04:05.550 --> 00:04:06.120 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:07.240 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: That's correct.

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:11.270 align:middle line:10%
And in looking back,
my understanding

00:04:11.270 --> 00:04:14.240 align:middle line:10%
is when you look at the
ancient philosophers who

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:17.950 align:middle line:10%
practiced either
alchemy or theurgy--

00:04:17.950 --> 00:04:20.170 align:middle line:10%
and I should really
define theurgy.

00:04:20.170 --> 00:04:25.160 align:middle line:10%
Theurgy, as used by the
Greeks, was individuals

00:04:25.160 --> 00:04:29.570 align:middle line:10%
who placed themselves in
position, through their actions

00:04:29.570 --> 00:04:32.070 align:middle line:10%
and their thoughts,
that they would

00:04:32.070 --> 00:04:34.700 align:middle line:10%
be a mirror to the
higher spheres,

00:04:34.700 --> 00:04:38.910 align:middle line:10%
to the gods and
goddesses or God.

00:04:38.910 --> 00:04:44.450 align:middle line:10%
So in other words, they would be
acting godlike on this planet,

00:04:44.450 --> 00:04:48.760 align:middle line:10%
and they would draw those forces
down from the higher spheres.

00:04:48.760 --> 00:04:53.030 align:middle line:84%
They would be a mirror of the
grander part of the universe.

00:04:53.030 --> 00:04:56.800 align:middle line:84%
Well, this was not
something that just happened

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:58.820 align:middle line:90%
with the snap of a finger.

00:04:58.820 --> 00:05:01.260 align:middle line:84%
This was something
that was a practice.

00:05:01.260 --> 00:05:03.510 align:middle line:90%
It was a philosophy of life.

00:05:03.510 --> 00:05:09.850 align:middle line:10%
It was an individual living
the life of an alchemist, which

00:05:09.850 --> 00:05:17.230 align:middle line:10%
would mean an individual who was
working at achieving something.

00:05:17.230 --> 00:05:19.820 align:middle line:84%
Every one of these
philosophers will tell you,

00:05:19.820 --> 00:05:24.730 align:middle line:84%
they were years and
years to accomplish it.

00:05:24.730 --> 00:05:26.710 align:middle line:90%
Many of them didn't reach it.

00:05:26.710 --> 00:05:30.540 align:middle line:84%
But the ones who did
always would say,

00:05:30.540 --> 00:05:36.270 align:middle line:84%
either an individual or
wisdom herself came to them,

00:05:36.270 --> 00:05:38.230 align:middle line:90%
and then everything opened up.

00:05:38.230 --> 00:05:41.850 align:middle line:84%
So we are going to continue
with this conversation,

00:05:41.850 --> 00:05:47.760 align:middle line:84%
and I will get into what does it
mean living the chemical life,

00:05:47.760 --> 00:05:55.070 align:middle line:84%
so that people will understand
it isn't some magical device

00:05:55.070 --> 00:05:57.480 align:middle line:90%
or object that you find.

00:05:57.480 --> 00:06:02.370 align:middle line:10%
It is a change of state
where an individual so

00:06:02.370 --> 00:06:07.690 align:middle line:10%
transforms themself, they
transcend the physical self.

00:06:07.690 --> 00:06:10.380 align:middle line:10%
That they reach a
very high state.

00:06:10.380 --> 00:06:13.230 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So what I'm
understanding out of that,

00:06:13.230 --> 00:06:15.300 align:middle line:84%
as you were saying toward
the beginning of it,

00:06:15.300 --> 00:06:17.690 align:middle line:84%
it's almost as though
they're finding

00:06:17.690 --> 00:06:20.875 align:middle line:90%
the resolution to duality.

00:06:20.875 --> 00:06:23.930 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: That is-- when you
look at the various chemical

00:06:23.930 --> 00:06:27.540 align:middle line:84%
paintings and graphs
that they have,

00:06:27.540 --> 00:06:33.140 align:middle line:84%
it is always showing this
combination of opposites.

00:06:33.140 --> 00:06:35.280 align:middle line:90%
Bringing the opposites together.

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:37.870 align:middle line:84%
Now, in alchemical
terms-- and you

00:06:37.870 --> 00:06:39.600 align:middle line:84%
have to remember,
in those days, they

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:43.930 align:middle line:84%
did not have the words for
unconscious, conscious,

00:06:43.930 --> 00:06:47.120 align:middle line:84%
subconscious, so
there were terms

00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:50.030 align:middle line:84%
that were used as a
parlance of the day

00:06:50.030 --> 00:06:55.150 align:middle line:84%
to try to explain this
combining of opposites.

00:06:55.150 --> 00:06:59.290 align:middle line:84%
That is really the alchemical
way, the hermetic marriage,

00:06:59.290 --> 00:07:03.890 align:middle line:84%
the masculine and the
feminine within an individual.

00:07:03.890 --> 00:07:07.800 align:middle line:10%
Now again, most of your
listeners are very, very savvy,

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:10.050 align:middle line:10%
and they understand
that within a male,

00:07:10.050 --> 00:07:13.050 align:middle line:10%
you do have the feminine
nature, you have a masculine.

00:07:13.050 --> 00:07:15.830 align:middle line:10%
And in the female,
it is the same.

00:07:15.830 --> 00:07:21.090 align:middle line:10%
It is this combining
of these opposites,

00:07:21.090 --> 00:07:25.730 align:middle line:10%
becoming one, that aligns
an individual to the higher

00:07:25.730 --> 00:07:29.970 align:middle line:10%
precepts, the greater
wisdom that is there.

00:07:29.970 --> 00:07:33.700 align:middle line:10%
But again, it is a practice.

00:07:33.700 --> 00:07:36.640 align:middle line:10%
It is a lifestyle.

00:07:36.640 --> 00:07:40.010 align:middle line:10%
I'm going to jump all the way
ahead to someone-- Ralph Waldo

00:07:40.010 --> 00:07:43.740 align:middle line:10%
Emerson, who is more of a
modern day philosopher, who

00:07:43.740 --> 00:07:46.510 align:middle line:10%
spoke about self-reliance.

00:07:46.510 --> 00:07:53.520 align:middle line:84%
It is-- those alchemists did not
depend on some outside source.

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:55.640 align:middle line:90%
They did not have their gurus.

00:07:55.640 --> 00:08:00.530 align:middle line:84%
They had people they admired,
but they had to do the work.

00:08:00.530 --> 00:08:04.820 align:middle line:84%
And the true alchemists
did the work.

00:08:04.820 --> 00:08:06.820 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Which is different
than having secrets

00:08:06.820 --> 00:08:11.070 align:middle line:84%
passed on to you, which is
only a stage in the process.

00:08:11.070 --> 00:08:16.680 align:middle line:84%
And I want to go into that,
because the notion of secrecy

00:08:16.680 --> 00:08:19.070 align:middle line:90%
has become a hot topic.

00:08:19.070 --> 00:08:19.570 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:08:19.570 --> 00:08:21.710 align:middle line:84%
Because we feel as though
our privacy's being

00:08:21.710 --> 00:08:24.170 align:middle line:84%
invaded on many levels
in this modern era,

00:08:24.170 --> 00:08:26.040 align:middle line:84%
because of technology
and so forth.

00:08:26.040 --> 00:08:29.260 align:middle line:84%
But then if you go further into
the conspiracy communities,

00:08:29.260 --> 00:08:30.900 align:middle line:84%
anything having
to do with secrecy

00:08:30.900 --> 00:08:33.929 align:middle line:84%
is inherently negative
or evil or there's

00:08:33.929 --> 00:08:36.370 align:middle line:90%
a controlling elite behind it.

00:08:36.370 --> 00:08:40.770 align:middle line:84%
Yet that was really critical
to the great teachings

00:08:40.770 --> 00:08:42.070 align:middle line:90%
in the time.

00:08:42.070 --> 00:08:45.840 align:middle line:84%
And I want you to take some
time explaining this to us.

00:08:45.840 --> 00:08:50.090 align:middle line:84%
What was originally intended
all the way through the times

00:08:50.090 --> 00:08:51.070 align:middle line:90%
to today?

00:08:51.070 --> 00:08:58.150 align:middle line:84%
Is it still relevant to have
these great, deep wisdoms

00:08:58.150 --> 00:09:01.200 align:middle line:90%
shared or kept secret?

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:04.260 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: I'm going to
start with an analogy that

00:09:04.260 --> 00:09:05.630 align:middle line:90%
is a little biblical.

00:09:05.630 --> 00:09:08.440 align:middle line:90%
Actually, it's a lot biblical.

00:09:08.440 --> 00:09:10.960 align:middle line:90%
Moses goes up to the mountain.

00:09:10.960 --> 00:09:13.430 align:middle line:84%
And I want people to
visualize Charlton Heston,

00:09:13.430 --> 00:09:14.825 align:middle line:90%
because it's all we see here.

00:09:14.825 --> 00:09:16.700 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: He cut a great
Moses on the screen.

00:09:16.700 --> 00:09:17.574 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: That's right.

00:09:17.574 --> 00:09:19.720 align:middle line:84%
So Moses goes up
to the mountain.

00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:21.880 align:middle line:84%
He's talking to
the burning bush.

00:09:21.880 --> 00:09:23.620 align:middle line:90%
He gets all this knowledge.

00:09:23.620 --> 00:09:26.730 align:middle line:84%
He's aligned with
the wisdom of God.

00:09:26.730 --> 00:09:30.300 align:middle line:84%
He ends up with a white
beard and white hair.

00:09:30.300 --> 00:09:32.370 align:middle line:90%
He comes down from the mountain.

00:09:32.370 --> 00:09:34.370 align:middle line:90%
He goes to the pharaoh.

00:09:34.370 --> 00:09:36.110 align:middle line:90%
Let my people go.

00:09:36.110 --> 00:09:43.260 align:middle line:84%
So he has his brother Aaron
cast his rod on the ground,

00:09:43.260 --> 00:09:45.950 align:middle line:90%
and it turns into a snake.

00:09:45.950 --> 00:09:48.360 align:middle line:90%
It was a white snake.

00:09:48.360 --> 00:09:52.620 align:middle line:84%
Now, most people would go,
ooh, that was really something.

00:09:52.620 --> 00:09:54.680 align:middle line:84%
But the pharaoh was
really not moved.

00:09:54.680 --> 00:09:59.500 align:middle line:84%
He tells his magicians to
cast their staves down.

00:09:59.500 --> 00:10:02.570 align:middle line:90%
They turned into three snakes.

00:10:02.570 --> 00:10:05.540 align:middle line:84%
Now, going by the movie,
so people can visualize,

00:10:05.540 --> 00:10:07.250 align:middle line:90%
there were three black snakes.

00:10:07.250 --> 00:10:09.880 align:middle line:84%
They were bigger
than the white snake,

00:10:09.880 --> 00:10:15.160 align:middle line:84%
but Moses' white snake slowly
swallowed all the other snakes.

00:10:15.160 --> 00:10:19.860 align:middle line:84%
And of course, the pharaoh's
court, then they went, ooh.

00:10:19.860 --> 00:10:21.370 align:middle line:90%
What is that telling us?

00:10:21.370 --> 00:10:23.840 align:middle line:84%
What it's telling
us is the following.

00:10:23.840 --> 00:10:29.520 align:middle line:84%
There is an energy that is
available to all people,

00:10:29.520 --> 00:10:34.050 align:middle line:84%
whether it is positive
or less than positive.

00:10:34.050 --> 00:10:36.830 align:middle line:84%
You don't have to be
a high mucky muck.

00:10:36.830 --> 00:10:40.090 align:middle line:84%
You don't have to be
spiritually evolved.

00:10:40.090 --> 00:10:42.740 align:middle line:90%
They did the same thing.

00:10:42.740 --> 00:10:47.560 align:middle line:84%
Their energy is there for
all use and for everybody.

00:10:47.560 --> 00:10:49.110 align:middle line:90%
Now, back to your question.

00:10:49.110 --> 00:10:51.680 align:middle line:90%
Why the secrecy at the time?

00:10:51.680 --> 00:10:56.740 align:middle line:84%
The secrecy was not
everybody understood that.

00:10:56.740 --> 00:10:59.270 align:middle line:84%
And so it was kept
more of a secret,

00:10:59.270 --> 00:11:05.740 align:middle line:84%
because if everybody realized
that they had this ability,

00:11:05.740 --> 00:11:10.110 align:middle line:84%
not everybody was schooled
in high enough ethics

00:11:10.110 --> 00:11:14.100 align:middle line:84%
to understand how
to use it properly.

00:11:14.100 --> 00:11:17.240 align:middle line:84%
I am not so sure, and I
don't mean to be judgmental,

00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:20.650 align:middle line:84%
but I don't know, in today's
society, how many people would

00:11:20.650 --> 00:11:26.320 align:middle line:84%
be schooled to also use some of
this knowledge in the highest,

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:29.480 align:middle line:90%
most ethical, loving manner.

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:30.520 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Very true.

00:11:30.520 --> 00:11:33.960 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: It is used
because it exists.

00:11:33.960 --> 00:11:36.930 align:middle line:10%
It is used because when an
individual like Walt Disney

00:11:36.930 --> 00:11:41.310 align:middle line:10%
decides, someday there's going
to be a Disneyland, he's using,

00:11:41.310 --> 00:11:45.490 align:middle line:10%
quote, "the secret," which
is really not a secret,

00:11:45.490 --> 00:11:47.790 align:middle line:10%
that the law of
attraction is there.

00:11:47.790 --> 00:11:53.370 align:middle line:84%
So these ancients felt this
was so powerful that they just

00:11:53.370 --> 00:11:56.840 align:middle line:84%
didn't want anybody
doing it unless they went

00:11:56.840 --> 00:11:59.030 align:middle line:90%
into the whole mystery school.

00:11:59.030 --> 00:12:02.250 align:middle line:84%
Now, that mystery school was
not like a 24 hour school

00:12:02.250 --> 00:12:04.020 align:middle line:90%
that you went in and out.

00:12:04.020 --> 00:12:04.880 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Right, it
was a lifetime process.

00:12:04.880 --> 00:12:06.296 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: It was a
lifetime process.

00:12:06.296 --> 00:12:08.930 align:middle line:84%
That even Pythagoras,
the great philosopher,

00:12:08.930 --> 00:12:13.980 align:middle line:84%
had to sit in front of temples
in Egypt for years and years

00:12:13.980 --> 00:12:17.550 align:middle line:84%
until they finally said,
maybe this guy's serious.

00:12:17.550 --> 00:12:18.940 align:middle line:90%
This is Pythagoras.

00:12:18.940 --> 00:12:22.490 align:middle line:84%
Maybe he's serious, and
we're going to let him in.

00:12:22.490 --> 00:12:27.470 align:middle line:84%
It is a philosophy of
life where an individual

00:12:27.470 --> 00:12:34.110 align:middle line:84%
is really schooled in how
to use the higher regimes

00:12:34.110 --> 00:12:36.310 align:middle line:90%
in the highest and best manner.

00:12:36.310 --> 00:12:38.600 align:middle line:84%
So that's the answer
to your first question,

00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:41.670 align:middle line:90%
why the secrecy.

00:12:41.670 --> 00:12:45.020 align:middle line:84%
Now, if we want to
continue on that tack,

00:12:45.020 --> 00:12:47.110 align:middle line:90%
is there a need for that today?

00:12:47.110 --> 00:12:52.890 align:middle line:84%
Well, really not, because
the secret is out.

00:12:52.890 --> 00:12:54.400 align:middle line:90%
It is there.

00:12:54.400 --> 00:12:56.830 align:middle line:90%
It has always been there.

00:12:56.830 --> 00:12:58.580 align:middle line:84%
Even though there
were mystery schools,

00:12:58.580 --> 00:13:01.052 align:middle line:84%
and these people were
threatened that they would die--

00:13:01.052 --> 00:13:03.260 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Let's talk about
Socrates in a moment, too.

00:13:03.260 --> 00:13:06.030 align:middle line:84%
Yes, they were under the threat
of death to reveal the secrets.

00:13:06.030 --> 00:13:06.905 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: It was death.

00:13:06.905 --> 00:13:09.130 align:middle line:84%
But let's get right
into Socrates.

00:13:09.130 --> 00:13:13.020 align:middle line:84%
Socrates could
reveal some of it,

00:13:13.020 --> 00:13:15.530 align:middle line:84%
because he never
took the sacred vow.

00:13:15.530 --> 00:13:17.950 align:middle line:84%
He did not go to
a mystery school.

00:13:17.950 --> 00:13:22.550 align:middle line:10%
And so he was revealing,
through his speech

00:13:22.550 --> 00:13:25.850 align:middle line:10%
and Plato's writing-- because
Socrates did not write,

00:13:25.850 --> 00:13:31.100 align:middle line:10%
but the Socratic dialogues was
written by his disciple, Plato.

00:13:31.100 --> 00:13:36.740 align:middle line:10%
But yes, he was revealing some
of these very, very important

00:13:36.740 --> 00:13:38.000 align:middle line:10%
precepts.

00:13:38.000 --> 00:13:40.740 align:middle line:84%
And that may be a
little bit down the line

00:13:40.740 --> 00:13:45.390 align:middle line:84%
from where we are of what were
they really teaching there.

00:13:45.390 --> 00:13:49.020 align:middle line:84%
But what we want to really lay
as a groundwork, Regina, is

00:13:49.020 --> 00:13:53.250 align:middle line:84%
that it wasn't a quick, you're
going to find the answer.

00:13:53.250 --> 00:13:58.250 align:middle line:84%
There's a magical note,
that when it's played,

00:13:58.250 --> 00:14:01.170 align:middle line:84%
all of a sudden you have
instant enlightenment.

00:14:01.170 --> 00:14:02.709 align:middle line:90%
It just doesn't work like that.

00:14:02.709 --> 00:14:03.250 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: No.

00:14:03.250 --> 00:14:08.000 align:middle line:84%
And some of these mystery
schools, in various forms,

00:14:08.000 --> 00:14:10.880 align:middle line:84%
some truer to the original
purpose than others,

00:14:10.880 --> 00:14:12.490 align:middle line:90%
still exist.

00:14:12.490 --> 00:14:17.780 align:middle line:84%
There are still people studying
these very pure ancient tenets.

00:14:17.780 --> 00:14:20.450 align:middle line:84%
But I would like
you to make comment

00:14:20.450 --> 00:14:22.530 align:middle line:84%
on that, because you
see mystery school here,

00:14:22.530 --> 00:14:26.230 align:middle line:84%
mystery school there, that's
not what we're talking

00:14:26.230 --> 00:14:27.700 align:middle line:90%
about in a lot of cases.

00:14:27.700 --> 00:14:29.990 align:middle line:84%
And help people understand
what the difference

00:14:29.990 --> 00:14:31.970 align:middle line:84%
may be when you see
an advertised "mystery

00:14:31.970 --> 00:14:36.460 align:middle line:84%
school" of one kind or
another versus genuine schools

00:14:36.460 --> 00:14:40.800 align:middle line:84%
of the tenets for life,
the understanding of life.

00:14:40.800 --> 00:14:42.950 align:middle line:10%
>>ROSS: You have a
term called esoteric,

00:14:42.950 --> 00:14:48.400 align:middle line:10%
which is the internal, and
exoteric, which is the outer.

00:14:48.400 --> 00:14:51.340 align:middle line:10%
The original Rosicrucians,
as an example,

00:14:51.340 --> 00:14:56.630 align:middle line:10%
was a secret organization where
virtually none of the members

00:14:56.630 --> 00:15:00.250 align:middle line:10%
were known, and it was
by invitation only.

00:15:00.250 --> 00:15:04.700 align:middle line:10%
Now, you have Rosicrucianism
in several different places,

00:15:04.700 --> 00:15:08.240 align:middle line:10%
where people can sign
up, they are admitted,

00:15:08.240 --> 00:15:09.740 align:middle line:10%
they take courses.

00:15:09.740 --> 00:15:12.020 align:middle line:84%
Now, I'm not picking
on Rosicrucianism,

00:15:12.020 --> 00:15:17.150 align:middle line:84%
I'm just commenting that a
lot of these original schools,

00:15:17.150 --> 00:15:20.100 align:middle line:84%
individuals had to
prove themselves

00:15:20.100 --> 00:15:26.260 align:middle line:84%
and were invited to partake
in some of this wisdom.

00:15:26.260 --> 00:15:28.330 align:middle line:84%
Going back at the
School of Crotona,

00:15:28.330 --> 00:15:33.780 align:middle line:84%
which was Pythagoras'
school around 500 BC,

00:15:33.780 --> 00:15:37.140 align:middle line:84%
it was a whole
curriculum of activities.

00:15:37.140 --> 00:15:42.990 align:middle line:84%
But he just didn't admit anybody
who signed up and paid a fee.

00:15:42.990 --> 00:15:45.940 align:middle line:84%
He really looked
at the individual,

00:15:45.940 --> 00:15:48.960 align:middle line:84%
to the extent that
he would make jokes

00:15:48.960 --> 00:15:51.540 align:middle line:84%
to see how the
individual laughed,

00:15:51.540 --> 00:15:56.480 align:middle line:84%
how the individual walked,
how the individual spoke,

00:15:56.480 --> 00:15:58.770 align:middle line:84%
how the individual
carried themselves

00:15:58.770 --> 00:16:00.970 align:middle line:90%
under various situations.

00:16:00.970 --> 00:16:03.360 align:middle line:84%
And of course, he
had a background

00:16:03.360 --> 00:16:06.490 align:middle line:84%
that he expected
mathematics and rhetoric

00:16:06.490 --> 00:16:08.300 align:middle line:90%
to be part of their background.

00:16:08.300 --> 00:16:14.420 align:middle line:84%
But he analyzed, is this
individual male or female?

00:16:14.420 --> 00:16:16.940 align:middle line:84%
And he was way
ahead of his time,

00:16:16.940 --> 00:16:22.710 align:middle line:84%
because women were treated
equally in his school.

00:16:22.710 --> 00:16:24.730 align:middle line:84%
He also had something
that was fascinating,

00:16:24.730 --> 00:16:29.710 align:middle line:84%
which was levels in his Academy
where students could not

00:16:29.710 --> 00:16:33.050 align:middle line:84%
speak for either three
or five years, which

00:16:33.050 --> 00:16:37.410 align:middle line:84%
meant they had to listen
to all of the teaching

00:16:37.410 --> 00:16:41.770 align:middle line:84%
without commenting,
without debating.

00:16:41.770 --> 00:16:45.730 align:middle line:84%
Five years for
their highest quote,

00:16:45.730 --> 00:16:52.130 align:middle line:84%
"initiates," so that they would
take in everything before they

00:16:52.130 --> 00:16:54.070 align:middle line:90%
would start arguing a point.

00:16:54.070 --> 00:16:57.740 align:middle line:84%
This is underlying what
our conversation up to now

00:16:57.740 --> 00:17:02.070 align:middle line:84%
has been about, and that
is, it is a lifestyle.

00:17:02.070 --> 00:17:04.569 align:middle line:90%
It is a philosophy of life.

00:17:04.569 --> 00:17:09.740 align:middle line:84%
Nowadays, somebody can join
quote, this "mystery school"

00:17:09.740 --> 00:17:14.430 align:middle line:84%
because Mr. or Mrs. X
says, "I am teaching

00:17:14.430 --> 00:17:16.420 align:middle line:90%
the wisdom of the ages.

00:17:16.420 --> 00:17:18.130 align:middle line:90%
This is the mystery school.

00:17:18.130 --> 00:17:19.819 align:middle line:90%
This is what you pay.

00:17:19.819 --> 00:17:21.710 align:middle line:84%
This is what you're
going to get.

00:17:21.710 --> 00:17:25.970 align:middle line:84%
And you can take level two
and level four and level six,

00:17:25.970 --> 00:17:29.850 align:middle line:84%
and I'm going to slowly
bring you to this point

00:17:29.850 --> 00:17:33.110 align:middle line:84%
where you are going to
have this great awareness."

00:17:33.110 --> 00:17:36.110 align:middle line:84%
The fallacies that I
have found, and this

00:17:36.110 --> 00:17:40.030 align:middle line:84%
is my understanding
and only my opinion,

00:17:40.030 --> 00:17:41.660 align:middle line:84%
is that very few of
these people who've

00:17:41.660 --> 00:17:43.700 align:middle line:84%
graduated from any
of these schools

00:17:43.700 --> 00:17:46.710 align:middle line:84%
is any different
than anybody else

00:17:46.710 --> 00:17:51.640 align:middle line:90%
who attends a beautiful school.

00:17:51.640 --> 00:17:54.330 align:middle line:90%
A music school, an art school.

00:17:54.330 --> 00:17:57.940 align:middle line:84%
These people who are attending
these mystery schools, what

00:17:57.940 --> 00:17:59.450 align:middle line:90%
are they doing?

00:17:59.450 --> 00:18:02.540 align:middle line:84%
Even the teachers
who are teaching.

00:18:02.540 --> 00:18:04.800 align:middle line:84%
I have been in this
field for 40 years.

00:18:04.800 --> 00:18:07.360 align:middle line:84%
I've been on the podiums
with a lot of people

00:18:07.360 --> 00:18:09.140 align:middle line:90%
who have written these books.

00:18:09.140 --> 00:18:12.182 align:middle line:84%
And they have one
persona to the public,

00:18:12.182 --> 00:18:13.890 align:middle line:84%
and then they have
another persona, where

00:18:13.890 --> 00:18:15.630 align:middle line:90%
they're telling me, oh my gosh.

00:18:15.630 --> 00:18:18.130 align:middle line:84%
I'm going under,
financially strapped.

00:18:18.130 --> 00:18:21.880 align:middle line:84%
But moments before, they're
teaching financial prosperity

00:18:21.880 --> 00:18:23.210 align:middle line:90%
and financial consciousness.

00:18:23.210 --> 00:18:24.950 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: There's
an incoherence.

00:18:24.950 --> 00:18:27.720 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: And this is
going to be a keynote

00:18:27.720 --> 00:18:29.920 align:middle line:90%
of my sharing with you.

00:18:29.920 --> 00:18:31.970 align:middle line:90%
It is the word integrity.

00:18:31.970 --> 00:18:36.160 align:middle line:90%
It is an integrity of being.

00:18:36.160 --> 00:18:40.430 align:middle line:84%
What you talk about
is how you walk.

00:18:40.430 --> 00:18:44.290 align:middle line:10%
What you say is how you act.

00:18:44.290 --> 00:18:50.060 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to define that as
either being in integrity

00:18:50.060 --> 00:18:53.080 align:middle line:90%
or being out of integrity.

00:18:53.080 --> 00:18:58.000 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, that's a very
practical description of what

00:18:58.000 --> 00:18:59.500 align:middle line:90%
integrity is for all of us.

00:18:59.500 --> 00:19:00.890 align:middle line:90%
Everybody can understand that.

00:19:00.890 --> 00:19:04.360 align:middle line:84%
But the thing is, we
seem to give a pass to it

00:19:04.360 --> 00:19:07.910 align:middle line:84%
with the spiritual community
and the religious community.

00:19:07.910 --> 00:19:11.660 align:middle line:84%
Oh, you know, so and so,
Tammy's crying because Jimmy's

00:19:11.660 --> 00:19:12.710 align:middle line:90%
whatever he's done.

00:19:12.710 --> 00:19:16.820 align:middle line:84%
And mascara runs, and
everyone-- oh, he's just a man.

00:19:16.820 --> 00:19:18.600 align:middle line:84%
You know, he's just
doing what men do.

00:19:18.600 --> 00:19:19.940 align:middle line:90%
We have to forgive him.

00:19:19.940 --> 00:19:22.489 align:middle line:84%
But you're saying,
yeah, we're all people.

00:19:22.489 --> 00:19:23.530 align:middle line:90%
We all have these things.

00:19:23.530 --> 00:19:25.859 align:middle line:84%
But you're saying, one
has to hold oneself

00:19:25.859 --> 00:19:27.400 align:middle line:84%
to a little higher
standard than that

00:19:27.400 --> 00:19:29.260 align:middle line:90%
if you're going to profess.

00:19:29.260 --> 00:19:30.980 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: That's the key point.

00:19:30.980 --> 00:19:32.760 align:middle line:90%
We're all seekers.

00:19:32.760 --> 00:19:38.150 align:middle line:84%
I love what Pythagoras
said about learning.

00:19:38.150 --> 00:19:42.690 align:middle line:84%
Pythagoras said, when I come
across those who I share with,

00:19:42.690 --> 00:19:46.720 align:middle line:90%
I call them brother and sister.

00:19:46.720 --> 00:19:50.650 align:middle line:84%
When I come upon those who I
meet that give me information,

00:19:50.650 --> 00:19:53.760 align:middle line:90%
I call them father or mother.

00:19:53.760 --> 00:19:58.150 align:middle line:84%
And when I come across as
those who I impart wisdom to,

00:19:58.150 --> 00:20:00.890 align:middle line:90%
I call them son and daughter.

00:20:00.890 --> 00:20:03.150 align:middle line:84%
This great
philosopher was always

00:20:03.150 --> 00:20:07.840 align:middle line:84%
open to learning and receiving
from others without saying,

00:20:07.840 --> 00:20:10.010 align:middle line:90%
I know it all.

00:20:10.010 --> 00:20:15.310 align:middle line:84%
So I, in my belief
system, hold anyone

00:20:15.310 --> 00:20:18.470 align:middle line:84%
up to a higher standard
who calls himself

00:20:18.470 --> 00:20:22.550 align:middle line:90%
a guru, a master, or a teacher.

00:20:22.550 --> 00:20:27.665 align:middle line:84%
Because they are
imparting this to others,

00:20:27.665 --> 00:20:29.040 align:middle line:84%
sending a lot of
them-- I'm going

00:20:29.040 --> 00:20:31.620 align:middle line:84%
to use the example of a
couple names used earlier--

00:20:31.620 --> 00:20:34.190 align:middle line:84%
they're sending other
people to hell and hellfire

00:20:34.190 --> 00:20:35.760 align:middle line:90%
and damnation.

00:20:35.760 --> 00:20:38.680 align:middle line:84%
But then when the
table is turned,

00:20:38.680 --> 00:20:41.090 align:middle line:84%
they don't live under
the same standard.

00:20:41.090 --> 00:20:45.220 align:middle line:84%
I have more respect for
somebody who is consistent,

00:20:45.220 --> 00:20:47.610 align:middle line:84%
whether I agree
with them or not,

00:20:47.610 --> 00:20:50.390 align:middle line:84%
than somebody who
is out of integrity.

00:20:50.390 --> 00:20:51.680 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I understand that.

00:20:51.680 --> 00:20:55.730 align:middle line:84%
I have a little note
written down here.

00:20:55.730 --> 00:20:58.271 align:middle line:84%
We already kind of blew
past Socrates, here,

00:20:58.271 --> 00:20:59.770 align:middle line:84%
but there was a
note here, I thought

00:20:59.770 --> 00:21:01.770 align:middle line:84%
it might be worth just
going back and revisiting

00:21:01.770 --> 00:21:04.550 align:middle line:84%
when it comes to Socrates
and his revealing of some

00:21:04.550 --> 00:21:08.240 align:middle line:84%
of the great mysterious
knowledge of the day.

00:21:08.240 --> 00:21:11.700 align:middle line:84%
And that was called, Socrates'
little demon, or daemon.

00:21:11.700 --> 00:21:13.070 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Yes.

00:21:13.070 --> 00:21:15.210 align:middle line:84%
And by the way, I
think I'm almost coming

00:21:15.210 --> 00:21:16.550 align:middle line:90%
across too serious, here.

00:21:16.550 --> 00:21:19.280 align:middle line:84%
We're going to have to let
people know, in a real life,

00:21:19.280 --> 00:21:21.182 align:middle line:90%
I'm a very fun-loving guy.

00:21:21.182 --> 00:21:22.140 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, you are.

00:21:22.140 --> 00:21:22.726 align:middle line:90%
Lethyl.

00:21:22.726 --> 00:21:24.600 align:middle line:84%
We will talk about lethyl
at some other time.

00:21:24.600 --> 00:21:27.120 align:middle line:84%
But let's talk about
Socrates' little daemon.

00:21:27.120 --> 00:21:27.840 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Yes.

00:21:27.840 --> 00:21:30.410 align:middle line:84%
Socrates wrote a
very interesting--

00:21:30.410 --> 00:21:35.210 align:middle line:84%
or spoke about a treatise
about a guidance mechanism

00:21:35.210 --> 00:21:37.660 align:middle line:90%
that he possessed.

00:21:37.660 --> 00:21:39.940 align:middle line:84%
And he referred
to it is a daemon.

00:21:39.940 --> 00:21:41.360 align:middle line:84%
Of course, now,
here's another one

00:21:41.360 --> 00:21:44.867 align:middle line:84%
of those terms that
has one meaning now

00:21:44.867 --> 00:21:46.200 align:middle line:90%
and another meaning in the past.

00:21:46.200 --> 00:21:47.450 align:middle line:90%
In the past, it was very kind.

00:21:47.450 --> 00:21:49.380 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But also
remember, it's D-A-E-M-O-N,

00:21:49.380 --> 00:21:50.670 align:middle line:90%
is the ancient one.

00:21:50.670 --> 00:21:52.630 align:middle line:84%
And please explain
what that means.

00:21:52.630 --> 00:21:53.250 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Right.

00:21:53.250 --> 00:21:57.660 align:middle line:84%
That represented a
higher order of beings

00:21:57.660 --> 00:22:01.870 align:middle line:84%
that were available
for individuals,

00:22:01.870 --> 00:22:05.670 align:middle line:84%
coming out of nature, and
also through individuals.

00:22:05.670 --> 00:22:09.820 align:middle line:10%
So Socrates referred
to this daemon

00:22:09.820 --> 00:22:13.950 align:middle line:10%
as it would always
give him advice

00:22:13.950 --> 00:22:18.670 align:middle line:10%
when he was about to do
something wrong or incorrect.

00:22:18.670 --> 00:22:22.820 align:middle line:84%
If he was going to do something
that was of high ethics

00:22:22.820 --> 00:22:26.260 align:middle line:84%
or not get him into
trouble, he wouldn't hear.

00:22:26.260 --> 00:22:29.300 align:middle line:84%
And that was his criteria
of knowing whether he

00:22:29.300 --> 00:22:30.930 align:middle line:90%
was on the right path or not.

00:22:30.930 --> 00:22:32.300 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: The little
daemon on his shoulder.

00:22:32.300 --> 00:22:33.966 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: A little
daemon on his shoulder.

00:22:33.966 --> 00:22:36.120 align:middle line:84%
And the story is told
that he was walking

00:22:36.120 --> 00:22:38.310 align:middle line:84%
with a group of
other philosophers,

00:22:38.310 --> 00:22:41.860 align:middle line:84%
and they were going to walk
along a particular street

00:22:41.860 --> 00:22:44.880 align:middle line:84%
that they had walked
along many, many times.

00:22:44.880 --> 00:22:48.130 align:middle line:84%
And his little daemon
said, don't do it.

00:22:48.130 --> 00:22:49.290 align:middle line:90%
Don't go this way.

00:22:49.290 --> 00:22:51.760 align:middle line:84%
So he told all these
other philosophers,

00:22:51.760 --> 00:22:55.240 align:middle line:84%
and they probably had been
drinking, or whatever.

00:22:55.240 --> 00:22:56.660 align:middle line:90%
And they continued on.

00:22:56.660 --> 00:22:57.590 align:middle line:90%
He didn't.

00:22:57.590 --> 00:23:03.100 align:middle line:84%
And a herd of swine ended
up coming down that street

00:23:03.100 --> 00:23:06.380 align:middle line:84%
and basically running over
the group of philosophers,

00:23:06.380 --> 00:23:07.870 align:middle line:90%
but not him.

00:23:07.870 --> 00:23:11.470 align:middle line:84%
And so he spoke
about it, whether it

00:23:11.470 --> 00:23:16.300 align:middle line:84%
was in the major aspects of
his life, or even something

00:23:16.300 --> 00:23:19.950 align:middle line:84%
about not being run
over by a herd of swine,

00:23:19.950 --> 00:23:23.260 align:middle line:90%
it is something that exists.

00:23:23.260 --> 00:23:28.260 align:middle line:10%
That is an aspect
