that's available to all of us

00:25:35.730 --> 00:25:37.520 align:middle line:90%
and what he did with it.

00:25:37.520 --> 00:25:43.490 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: JR Newton was a healer
that lived in the 1800s.

00:25:43.490 --> 00:25:45.350 align:middle line:84%
In lectures I've done
around the world,

00:25:45.350 --> 00:25:48.520 align:middle line:84%
I have asked how many people
have heard of JR Newton,

00:25:48.520 --> 00:25:51.490 align:middle line:84%
and nobody has ever
raised their hand.

00:25:51.490 --> 00:25:53.990 align:middle line:84%
This is an individual
who was in the United

00:25:53.990 --> 00:26:03.330 align:middle line:84%
States who cured or rectified
the diseases of 250,000 people.

00:26:03.330 --> 00:26:10.320 align:middle line:84%
Those healings where attested to
by mayors, governors, sheriffs,

00:26:10.320 --> 00:26:13.160 align:middle line:90%
lawyers, newspaper editors.

00:26:13.160 --> 00:26:16.580 align:middle line:84%
People were brought to him
who were completely paralyzed,

00:26:16.580 --> 00:26:20.640 align:middle line:84%
with withered legs
for 15 to 20 years.

00:26:20.640 --> 00:26:22.770 align:middle line:90%
All sorts of ailments.

00:26:22.770 --> 00:26:26.560 align:middle line:84%
And in 10 to 15
minutes, they walked out

00:26:26.560 --> 00:26:30.020 align:middle line:84%
of his presence
perfectly normal,

00:26:30.020 --> 00:26:32.750 align:middle line:84%
as if they had
never had a problem.

00:26:32.750 --> 00:26:39.970 align:middle line:84%
And his philosophy, his mode
of therapy, was a real secret.

00:26:39.970 --> 00:26:42.451 align:middle line:90%
It was called love.

00:26:42.451 --> 00:26:43.450 align:middle line:90%
His philosophy was love.

00:26:43.450 --> 00:26:45.366 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Most people
would say at this point,

00:26:45.366 --> 00:26:47.900 align:middle line:84%
was it their faith in
his love, or was it

00:26:47.900 --> 00:26:52.650 align:middle line:84%
his ability to project that very
high, clear, clean frequency

00:26:52.650 --> 00:26:53.487 align:middle line:90%
into their being?

00:26:53.487 --> 00:26:54.320 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: It was both.

00:26:54.320 --> 00:27:02.360 align:middle line:84%
Because faith is established
when somebody has this feeling

00:27:02.360 --> 00:27:05.080 align:middle line:84%
that something is
going to happen.

00:27:05.080 --> 00:27:07.780 align:middle line:84%
Not that they think
it's going to happen,

00:27:07.780 --> 00:27:09.670 align:middle line:90%
it is going to happen.

00:27:09.670 --> 00:27:14.510 align:middle line:84%
And JR Newton said, to
the matter of healing,

00:27:14.510 --> 00:27:17.730 align:middle line:84%
it is a demonstration
of the power of love.

00:27:17.730 --> 00:27:19.800 align:middle line:90%
I tell someone I love them.

00:27:19.800 --> 00:27:21.730 align:middle line:90%
I show them I love them.

00:27:21.730 --> 00:27:24.670 align:middle line:90%
And the disease must depart.

00:27:24.670 --> 00:27:28.540 align:middle line:84%
Now, there are people who'd
go on to say, I really love.

00:27:28.540 --> 00:27:30.040 align:middle line:90%
I'm the epitome of love.

00:27:30.040 --> 00:27:32.950 align:middle line:90%
But you don't feel it.

00:27:32.950 --> 00:27:35.940 align:middle line:90%
JR Newton exuded love.

00:27:35.940 --> 00:27:39.940 align:middle line:84%
It was said that nobody
could argue in this presence.

00:27:39.940 --> 00:27:44.000 align:middle line:84%
It was stated that his
eyes and his vision,

00:27:44.000 --> 00:27:46.719 align:middle line:84%
when he gazed at you,
I should say his gaze--

00:27:46.719 --> 00:27:47.760 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Beautiful face.

00:27:47.760 --> 00:27:48.220 align:middle line:90%
Very pure.

00:27:48.220 --> 00:27:48.720 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Yes.

00:27:48.720 --> 00:27:52.450 align:middle line:84%
Was so overwhelming
that people just

00:27:52.450 --> 00:27:57.680 align:middle line:84%
felt and knew that something
beautiful was going to happen.

00:27:57.680 --> 00:28:03.170 align:middle line:84%
And in this beauty that
this man exuded with love,

00:28:03.170 --> 00:28:05.150 align:middle line:90%
these healings took place.

00:28:05.150 --> 00:28:07.910 align:middle line:84%
Now, he stated on
his failures-- he

00:28:07.910 --> 00:28:11.360 align:middle line:84%
had 250,000 successes--
his failures came

00:28:11.360 --> 00:28:15.040 align:middle line:84%
because people didn't
believe that he could do it.

00:28:15.040 --> 00:28:19.390 align:middle line:84%
They were so indoctrinated and
believed that it wasn't going

00:28:19.390 --> 00:28:21.120 align:middle line:90%
to happen, it didn't.

00:28:21.120 --> 00:28:25.760 align:middle line:84%
But he lived the life
for his entire life.

00:28:25.760 --> 00:28:27.630 align:middle line:90%
Now, what does that mean?

00:28:27.630 --> 00:28:31.130 align:middle line:84%
We're back to-- because I could
say that is a form of alchemy.

00:28:31.130 --> 00:28:34.480 align:middle line:84%
He had the Philosopher's
Stone, because what

00:28:34.480 --> 00:28:38.760 align:middle line:84%
we're going to find out is
the Philosopher's Stone just

00:28:38.760 --> 00:28:40.930 align:middle line:90%
may be love.

00:28:40.930 --> 00:28:44.580 align:middle line:84%
That this ultimate that all
these individuals sought,

00:28:44.580 --> 00:28:47.170 align:middle line:84%
all these alchemists
wrote about,

00:28:47.170 --> 00:28:53.090 align:middle line:84%
was not a stone
outside or inside.

00:28:53.090 --> 00:28:56.200 align:middle line:90%
It was a vibration of love.

00:28:56.200 --> 00:29:01.290 align:middle line:84%
And this love solidified
in them that they--

00:29:01.290 --> 00:29:02.600 align:middle line:90%
let's use an analogy.

00:29:02.600 --> 00:29:07.170 align:middle line:84%
Love is like the genie
in Aladdin's lamp.

00:29:07.170 --> 00:29:13.300 align:middle line:84%
It is through love that the rod
of the wonder workers exists.

00:29:13.300 --> 00:29:18.020 align:middle line:84%
So there are some depictions,
friezes, of Jesus.

00:29:18.020 --> 00:29:19.880 align:middle line:84%
Somebody on another
one of your shows

00:29:19.880 --> 00:29:22.800 align:middle line:90%
mentioned Jesus holding a rod.

00:29:22.800 --> 00:29:26.880 align:middle line:84%
It just may be that that rod was
love, because how else can you

00:29:26.880 --> 00:29:32.730 align:middle line:84%
