emanating and touching another,

00:29:32.730 --> 00:29:37.220 align:middle line:84%
except by showing a
magical rod of love?

00:29:37.220 --> 00:29:40.410 align:middle line:84%
And JR Newton
exhibited it, which

00:29:40.410 --> 00:29:43.770 align:middle line:84%
