00:30:01.900 --> 00:30:04.534 align:middle line:84%
and they read this book
over and over and over--

00:30:04.534 --> 00:30:06.200 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You're
referring to the Bible.

00:30:06.200 --> 00:30:07.500 align:middle line:90%
The New Testament, yeah?

00:30:07.500 --> 00:30:08.840 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Yes, the Bible.

00:30:08.840 --> 00:30:10.420 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:30:10.420 --> 00:30:16.260 align:middle line:84%
Why are people not demonstrating
and living these precepts?

00:30:16.260 --> 00:30:19.350 align:middle line:84%
Now, somebody may pop
up and say, no, no.

00:30:19.350 --> 00:30:21.560 align:middle line:90%
I do live these precepts.

00:30:21.560 --> 00:30:23.990 align:middle line:10%
I profess in the
name of so and so.

00:30:23.990 --> 00:30:25.760 align:middle line:10%
