No.

00:30:27.080 --> 00:30:33.810 align:middle line:10%
Jesus laid out a complete
lifestyle of love and beauty.

00:30:33.810 --> 00:30:36.340 align:middle line:84%
And he was in
integrity all the time.

00:30:36.340 --> 00:30:37.040 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:30:37.040 --> 00:30:39.590 align:middle line:84%
Now, people don't need me
to say he was in integrity,

00:30:39.590 --> 00:30:41.360 align:middle line:90%
