00:30:41.360 --> 00:30:46.650 align:middle line:84%
He worked with people who
were quote, "sinners."

00:30:46.650 --> 00:30:48.770 align:middle line:84%
He worked with the good,
he worked with the bad.

00:30:48.770 --> 00:30:52.040 align:middle line:84%
He didn't pick and choose
who he was working with.

00:30:52.040 --> 00:30:54.407 align:middle line:84%
All individuals
who were in need.

00:30:54.407 --> 00:30:55.990 align:middle line:84%
And by the way, if
you have a wedding,

00:30:55.990 --> 00:30:59.090 align:middle line:84%
