brilliant individuals, who

00:31:10.060 --> 00:31:15.940 align:middle line:84%
argued with rabbis at
13, never write anything?

00:31:15.940 --> 00:31:20.890 align:middle line:84%
He had to be smart enough, or
he could not have been debating.

00:31:20.890 --> 00:31:23.930 align:middle line:84%
According to records, he
