00:31:23.930 --> 00:31:26.370 align:middle line:84%
He drew something in the
sand when they were stoning

00:31:26.370 --> 00:31:30.330 align:middle line:90%
the harlot and then erased it.

00:31:30.330 --> 00:31:35.480 align:middle line:84%
My understanding,
my belief is, he

00:31:35.480 --> 00:31:40.400 align:middle line:84%
wrote because the written word
will always be misinterpreted,

00:31:40.400 --> 00:31:42.930 align:middle line:90%
but examples not.

00:31:42.930 --> 00:31:46.570 align:middle line:84%
And now we're back
to the alchemists.

00:31:46.570 --> 00:31:48.470 align:middle line:90%
It was by example.

00:31:48.470 --> 00:31:51.330 align:middle line:84%
It was by physically
experiencing

00:31:51.330 --> 00:31:53.960 align:middle line:84%
what was taking place
in those ancient mystery

00:31:53.960 --> 00:31:59.310 align:middle line:84%
schools, a thorough
understanding of bypassing

00:31:59.310 --> 00:32:05.330 align:middle line:84%
the conscious mind and reaching
higher states where the greater

00:32:05.330 --> 00:32:07.666 align:middle line:90%
illumination was taking place.

00:32:07.666 --> 00:32:10.260 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And this,
