can neutralize everything
and anything instantly.

00:35:10.859 --> 00:35:12.400 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's the
highest frequency.

00:35:12.400 --> 00:35:14.100 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: The highest frequency.

00:35:14.100 --> 00:35:16.040 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And that
does trump everything,

00:35:16.040 --> 00:35:18.960 align:middle line:84%
just as you were telling
about the three black snakes

00:35:18.960 --> 00:35:21.120 align:middle line:90%
and the one white snake.

00:35:21.120 --> 00:35:24.770 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: The positive in
love always will supersede.

00:35:24.770 --> 00:35:27.440 align:middle line:84%
That was the end of
that little story

00:35:27.440 --> 00:35:29.840 align:middle line:84%
that people kind of
blow through with Moses.

00:35:29.840 --> 00:35:31.230 align:middle line:90%
Like, wait a minute.

00:35:31.230 --> 00:35:32.860 align:middle line:90%
You've just come from God.

00:35:32.860 --> 00:35:34.770 align:middle line:84%
You're just come from
this interaction.

00:35:34.770 --> 00:35:38.280 align:middle line:84%
You have all the power, and
you go and do something,

00:35:38.280 --> 00:35:42.270 align:middle line:84%
and the other people
were able to do it also.

00:35:42.270 --> 00:35:47.650 align:middle line:84%
So could it be that you
are not necessarily given,

00:35:47.650 --> 00:35:54.320 align:middle line:84%
from God or the higher source,
the secret of doing something.

00:35:54.320 --> 00:35:57.650 align:middle line:90%
It is a wisdom of how to use it.

00:35:57.650 --> 00:36:01.859 align:middle line:84%
And that is the difference
between knowledge and wisdom.

00:36:01.859 --> 00:36:02.400 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:36:02.400 --> 00:36:05.920 align:middle line:84%
Now have we anything more
at this moment to say about,

00:36:05.920 --> 00:36:09.030 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to call it
the alchemy of love.

00:36:09.030 --> 00:36:14.080 align:middle line:84%
The thing that transcends,
transforms, and alters.

00:36:14.080 --> 00:36:18.920 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: I would say that we
can never talk enough about it.

00:36:18.920 --> 00:36:24.490 align:middle line:84%
I believe that in order for
people to really get it,

00:36:24.490 --> 00:36:28.500 align:middle line:84%
we need to continue on
with explaining examples

00:36:28.500 --> 00:36:30.720 align:middle line:90%
of how pertinent it is.

00:36:30.720 --> 00:36:33.530 align:middle line:84%
Because people out there,
especially the ones

00:36:33.530 --> 00:36:36.680 align:middle line:84%
who have bought into
courses and gurus

00:36:36.680 --> 00:36:42.030 align:middle line:84%
and teachers, when we say
love, it sounds too easy.

00:36:42.030 --> 00:36:43.160 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It sounds trite.

00:36:43.160 --> 00:36:46.660 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: It sounds trite,
because we've made love trite.

00:36:46.660 --> 00:36:52.560 align:middle line:84%
And you also have been through
Germany, so you'll understand.

00:36:52.560 --> 00:36:56.560 align:middle line:84%
In the United States,
love is called love.

00:36:56.560 --> 00:36:59.186 align:middle line:84%
But in Germany, there may
be 13 or 14 definitions.

00:36:59.186 --> 00:37:00.185 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Same in Greek.

00:37:00.185 --> 00:37:00.685 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:37:00.685 --> 00:37:05.210 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: Because I could
say, I love my car.

00:37:05.210 --> 00:37:06.990 align:middle line:90%
Honey, I love you.

00:37:06.990 --> 00:37:11.260 align:middle line:84%
I'm using the same word,
which is that love I--

00:37:11.260 --> 00:37:12.430 align:middle line:90%
it's the word love.

00:37:12.430 --> 00:37:13.690 align:middle line:90%
But it's more defined.

00:37:13.690 --> 00:37:15.731 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But qualitatively,
it's very different.

00:37:15.731 --> 00:37:20.140 align:middle line:84%
And we as a species, most
of us know how to love.

00:37:20.140 --> 00:37:22.120 align:middle line:84%
We know it when
we see our child.

00:37:22.120 --> 00:37:25.330 align:middle line:84%
The first moment we see a
child after their birth,

00:37:25.330 --> 00:37:27.360 align:middle line:84%
there is this
overwhelming thing that

00:37:27.360 --> 00:37:29.230 align:middle line:90%
happens to most individuals.

00:37:29.230 --> 00:37:31.990 align:middle line:84%
Which is, again, that
pure love that's not

00:37:31.990 --> 00:37:35.370 align:middle line:84%
assigned to any specific
traits or other values.

00:37:35.370 --> 00:37:40.120 align:middle line:84%
And yet, we let
ourselves off the hook

00:37:40.120 --> 00:37:42.350 align:middle line:90%
in terms of our lower behavior.

00:37:42.350 --> 00:37:46.130 align:middle line:84%
And we've fallen into
very sloppy habits

00:37:46.130 --> 00:37:50.890 align:middle line:84%
around holding on to the
need to indict on some level.

00:37:50.890 --> 00:37:54.950 align:middle line:84%
To create other
and us, when if we

00:37:54.950 --> 00:37:56.870 align:middle line:84%
could just discipline
ourselves for a moment--

00:37:56.870 --> 00:37:57.750 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Ah.

00:37:57.750 --> 00:38:00.180 align:middle line:84%
Now you just said
the magic word.

00:38:00.180 --> 00:38:00.950 align:middle line:90%
Discipline.

00:38:00.950 --> 00:38:02.490 align:middle line:90%
That means it takes work.

00:38:02.490 --> 00:38:03.980 align:middle line:90%
It takes an effort.

00:38:03.980 --> 00:38:09.720 align:middle line:84%
It takes a conscious effort
until it becomes unconscious

00:38:09.720 --> 00:38:11.930 align:middle line:90%
that you just are it.

00:38:11.930 --> 00:38:16.090 align:middle line:84%
So you just really
described why there

00:38:16.090 --> 00:38:19.340 align:middle line:84%
was a need for those
schools in the ancient time.

00:38:19.340 --> 00:38:23.050 align:middle line:84%
Because it isn't something
that you just snap your finger,

00:38:23.050 --> 00:38:27.130 align:middle line:84%
and you find that magic elixir,
and you find that magic stone,

00:38:27.130 --> 00:38:29.270 align:middle line:90%
and you find the magic rod.

00:38:29.270 --> 00:38:31.310 align:middle line:90%
It is a discipline.

00:38:31.310 --> 00:38:33.820 align:middle line:90%
It is work.

00:38:33.820 --> 00:38:36.640 align:middle line:84%
Plato and Socrates, I put
them, obviously, together,

00:38:36.640 --> 00:38:41.960 align:middle line:84%
because Plato described his
conversations with Socrates.

00:38:41.960 --> 00:38:47.230 align:middle line:10%
"The Symposium" that they
have written, "The Banquet,"

00:38:47.230 --> 00:38:50.980 align:middle line:10%
is one of the more
profound dialogues.

00:38:50.980 --> 00:38:53.980 align:middle line:84%
Because in it, it
talks about love.

00:38:53.980 --> 00:38:57.040 align:middle line:84%
It talks about
different types of love.

00:38:57.040 --> 00:39:02.870 align:middle line:84%
It is actually discussing what
our conversation has been.

00:39:02.870 --> 00:39:08.530 align:middle line:84%
And several philosophers,
the Neo-Platonists said,

00:39:08.530 --> 00:39:12.660 align:middle line:84%
their reading of "The
Banquet" and "The Symposium,"

00:39:12.660 --> 00:39:16.240 align:middle line:84%
which it was called
either one, gave them

00:39:16.240 --> 00:39:20.050 align:middle line:84%
the key to reach the
higher enlightenment

00:39:20.050 --> 00:39:22.360 align:middle line:90%
that they experienced.

00:39:22.360 --> 00:39:24.560 align:middle line:90%
They weren't mixing chemicals.

00:39:24.560 --> 00:39:27.170 align:middle line:84%
They weren't doing
outer experiments.

00:39:27.170 --> 00:39:31.540 align:middle line:84%
But they had this oneness
with the Supreme Source.

00:39:31.540 --> 00:39:37.800 align:middle line:84%
Because within that text was
what was taking place, partly,

00:39:37.800 --> 00:39:39.400 align:middle line:90%
in those mystery schools.

00:39:39.400 --> 00:39:42.370 align:middle line:84%
So the wisdom has
always been around

00:39:42.370 --> 00:39:44.750 align:middle line:90%
if people know where to look.

00:39:44.750 --> 00:39:49.540 align:middle line:84%
But it's the ego and
it's the mystery.

00:39:49.540 --> 00:39:53.230 align:middle line:10%
If I go and attend this course
that this person's doing,

00:39:53.230 --> 00:39:56.000 align:middle line:10%
I am going to have something
over my friend here,

00:39:56.000 --> 00:39:59.310 align:middle line:10%
because I am being
taught the secret wisdom.

00:39:59.310 --> 00:40:03.170 align:middle line:84%
I am getting the
arcana, the unknown.

00:40:03.170 --> 00:40:06.670 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That is the roadblock
to that essential thing

00:40:06.670 --> 00:40:09.570 align:middle line:90%
we call love, though.

00:40:09.570 --> 00:40:12.990 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: I should be interviewing
you, because you have it down.

00:40:12.990 --> 00:40:14.410 align:middle line:90%
It is the block.

00:40:14.410 --> 00:40:16.230 align:middle line:90%
It is the block.

00:40:16.230 --> 00:40:19.770 align:middle line:10%
It is a block that
we are so much

00:40:19.770 --> 00:40:27.250 align:middle line:10%
looking to get, to find, to
own, that we have forgotten

00:40:27.250 --> 00:40:30.020 align:middle line:10%
what the old teachings were.

00:40:30.020 --> 00:40:33.010 align:middle line:84%
The more you give,
the more you receive.

00:40:33.010 --> 00:40:35.160 align:middle line:90%
It is an endless supply.

00:40:35.160 --> 00:40:39.540 align:middle line:84%
And I personally, in
my understanding-- now,

00:40:39.540 --> 00:40:41.990 align:middle line:84%
I keep using that
phrase, because I am not

00:40:41.990 --> 00:40:46.120 align:middle line:84%
going to dogmatically say, I
know, and this is the way--

00:40:46.120 --> 00:40:50.960 align:middle line:84%
but my understanding
is that each of us

00:40:50.960 --> 00:40:55.910 align:middle line:84%
has a direct link with
the higher sources,

00:40:55.910 --> 00:41:00.040 align:middle line:84%
with the greater
wisdom within us.

00:41:00.040 --> 00:41:05.920 align:middle line:10%
And if there truly is a
loving mother/father up there,

00:41:05.920 --> 00:41:09.730 align:middle line:10%
it should be so
easy for us to find

00:41:09.730 --> 00:41:16.710 align:middle line:10%
and not some mysterious, buried,
only certain people possess,

00:41:16.710 --> 00:41:18.270 align:middle line:10%
only they know.

00:41:18.270 --> 00:41:21.625 align:middle line:84%
Because no parent down
here would do that

00:41:21.625 --> 00:41:23.550 align:middle line:90%
to their young kids.

00:41:23.550 --> 00:41:27.150 align:middle line:84%
To have them go and try
to dig and find an answer,

00:41:27.150 --> 00:41:31.640 align:middle line:84%
losing time, and then have
to spend an eternity in hell.

00:41:31.640 --> 00:41:34.720 align:middle line:84%
So if a regular
parent is like that,

00:41:34.720 --> 00:41:40.130 align:middle line:84%
I expect my mother/father up
there to be just as loving.

00:41:40.130 --> 00:41:43.940 align:middle line:84%
And is it possible
that the alchemical key

00:41:43.940 --> 00:41:46.220 align:middle line:90%
is beauty and love?

00:41:46.220 --> 00:41:49.050 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That's what I was
just going to ask you next.

00:41:49.050 --> 00:41:51.860 align:middle line:84%
Because a key element
here is beauty.

00:41:51.860 --> 00:41:55.230 align:middle line:84%
And we don't-- and we're
not talking about the cover

00:41:55.230 --> 00:41:57.130 align:middle line:90%
of "Elle" magazine beauty.

00:41:57.130 --> 00:42:00.190 align:middle line:84%
We're talking about beauty
in the most sublime sense.

00:42:00.190 --> 00:42:03.630 align:middle line:84%
As you say, it is
the partner of love.

00:42:03.630 --> 00:42:06.750 align:middle line:84%
So let's speak about
beauty by this definition.

00:42:06.750 --> 00:42:11.370 align:middle line:84%
And where beauty was
put on a pedestal

00:42:11.370 --> 00:42:15.090 align:middle line:84%
among the great philosophers and
spiritual leaders, so to speak,

00:42:15.090 --> 00:42:15.820 align:middle line:90%
of the day.

00:42:15.820 --> 00:42:19.450 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: One of the important
tenets from the Greeks

00:42:19.450 --> 00:42:21.050 align:middle line:90%
was the following.

00:42:21.050 --> 00:42:25.300 align:middle line:84%
The one, the good,
and the beautiful.

00:42:25.300 --> 00:42:26.630 align:middle line:90%
And what did that mean?

00:42:26.630 --> 00:42:28.100 align:middle line:10%
The one is very obvious.

00:42:28.100 --> 00:42:31.460 align:middle line:84%
It's one, one
all-encompassing all.

00:42:31.460 --> 00:42:37.210 align:middle line:84%
The word good, for the
ancients, meant everything works

00:42:37.210 --> 00:42:38.740 align:middle line:90%
in integrity.

00:42:38.740 --> 00:42:43.860 align:middle line:84%
And if you do something in
nature in the world one time,

00:42:43.860 --> 00:42:45.870 align:middle line:84%
you are going to
get an effect that

00:42:45.870 --> 00:42:48.850 align:middle line:90%
is consistent all the time.

00:42:48.850 --> 00:42:51.980 align:middle line:84%
If you break a
law of nature, you

00:42:51.980 --> 00:42:55.920 align:middle line:84%
are going to reap
a certain penalty.

00:42:55.920 --> 00:42:58.240 align:middle line:84%
You are going to reap
a certain lesson.

00:42:58.240 --> 00:43:00.780 align:middle line:84%
And that would happen
over and over and over.

00:43:00.780 --> 00:43:04.340 align:middle line:84%
So the ancients
said, that's good.

00:43:04.340 --> 00:43:07.890 align:middle line:10%
Even if the result was
bad, Regina, it's good.

00:43:07.890 --> 00:43:10.360 align:middle line:10%
Because that means
if I go this way,

00:43:10.360 --> 00:43:12.050 align:middle line:10%
this is going to be the result.

00:43:12.050 --> 00:43:12.470 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You will
learn the truth.

00:43:12.470 --> 00:43:15.140 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: You are going to learn
that lesson and the truth.

00:43:15.140 --> 00:43:18.990 align:middle line:90%
And the third tenet was beauty.

00:43:18.990 --> 00:43:24.550 align:middle line:84%
Now, beauty, of course, people
can sit here and ruminize

00:43:24.550 --> 00:43:28.930 align:middle line:84%
over and over, no, beauty means
this, and beauty means that.

00:43:28.930 --> 00:43:33.120 align:middle line:84%
Beauty is referring to an
integrity of the parts.

00:43:33.120 --> 00:43:36.530 align:middle line:90%
It is that everything fits in.

00:43:36.530 --> 00:43:40.240 align:middle line:84%
That it is
aesthetically beautiful.

00:43:40.240 --> 00:43:43.160 align:middle line:84%
The Greeks would not allow
any irregular shapes.

00:43:43.160 --> 00:43:46.340 align:middle line:84%
They didn't allow, at
a certain time, music

00:43:46.340 --> 00:43:47.880 align:middle line:90%
with discordant notes.

00:43:47.880 --> 00:43:55.180 align:middle line:84%
Because that interruption
of the normal flow,

00:43:55.180 --> 00:44:02.050 align:middle line:84%
the integrity of something,
a building, an environment,

00:44:02.050 --> 00:44:06.430 align:middle line:84%
was so disrupting, it
stopped you from the flow.

00:44:06.430 --> 00:44:09.840 align:middle line:84%
Now, this of course we
could make a whole show on.

00:44:09.840 --> 00:44:13.800 align:middle line:84%
But the ancients believed
that there were founts

00:44:13.800 --> 00:44:16.590 align:middle line:90%
of wisdom, beauty, truth.

00:44:16.590 --> 00:44:21.510 align:middle line:84%
Plato, when he spoke about
the ideal, that sphere,

00:44:21.510 --> 00:44:26.410 align:middle line:84%
there was an ideal coming
from the higher cosmos,

00:44:26.410 --> 00:44:29.720 align:middle line:84%
by gradations, down
to our Earth plane.

00:44:29.720 --> 00:44:32.320 align:middle line:10%
And if we mirrored
things down here,

00:44:32.320 --> 00:44:36.700 align:middle line:10%
we were connected to those
tremendous founts of wisdom.

00:44:36.700 --> 00:44:41.200 align:middle line:84%
So they kept beauty here
because it aligned you

00:44:41.200 --> 00:44:45.030 align:middle line:84%
with the beauty coming
from the higher spheres,

00:44:45.030 --> 00:44:48.405 align:middle line:90%
from that state of perfection.

00:44:48.405 --> 00:44:50.280 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And also that
state of equilibrium.

00:44:50.280 --> 00:44:54.260 align:middle line:84%
And when you look to the sacred
geometry throughout the ages,

00:44:54.260 --> 00:44:56.740 align:middle line:84%
there's always an
equilibrium in this geometry.

00:44:56.740 --> 00:44:59.620 align:middle line:84%
And you're bringing up something
that triggered a memory

00:44:59.620 --> 00:45:02.760 align:middle line:84%
of something else, which was--
and I won't go into any great

00:45:02.760 --> 00:45:04.449 align:middle line:90%
detail, but it is in the--

00:45:04.449 --> 00:45:05.740 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Regina, it's your show.

00:45:05.740 --> 00:45:06.531 align:middle line:90%
You go into detail.

00:45:06.531 --> 00:45:07.340 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: No, no.

00:45:07.340 --> 00:45:10.360 align:middle line:84%
It's in the congressional
record in January of 1964,

00:45:10.360 --> 00:45:13.590 align:middle line:84%
and it had to do with the--
this is a long, drawn-out thing

00:45:13.590 --> 00:45:20.410 align:middle line:84%
about a congressional committee
that was formed to hear out

00:45:20.410 --> 00:45:24.179 align:middle line:84%
the findings of a woman
who had essentially had-- I

00:45:24.179 --> 00:45:26.470 align:middle line:84%
don't think it was her, I
think she had others doing it

00:45:26.470 --> 00:45:30.450 align:middle line:84%
on her behalf-- infiltrated
the "communist" agenda here

00:45:30.450 --> 00:45:33.110 align:middle line:84%
on the planet,
especially in America.

00:45:33.110 --> 00:45:35.410 align:middle line:84%
And but one-- that's
here nor there.

00:45:35.410 --> 00:45:36.200 align:middle line:90%
That's political.

00:45:36.200 --> 00:45:37.430 align:middle line:90%
But not really.

00:45:37.430 --> 00:45:39.470 align:middle line:84%
One of the things that
came out of it that was,

00:45:39.470 --> 00:45:42.070 align:middle line:84%
to me, the most shocking
of the 47 points

00:45:42.070 --> 00:45:44.050 align:middle line:84%
that were made in
that hearing, was

00:45:44.050 --> 00:45:46.490 align:middle line:84%
that there would be
a concerted effort

00:45:46.490 --> 00:45:51.280 align:middle line:84%
to create disharmony
and asymmetry in art

00:45:51.280 --> 00:45:57.200 align:middle line:84%
to start creating a
disequilibrium amongst society

00:45:57.200 --> 00:45:59.930 align:middle line:84%
at large to make us
more manageable and more

00:45:59.930 --> 00:46:01.260 align:middle line:90%
controllable.

00:46:01.260 --> 00:46:03.860 align:middle line:90%
And it's so interesting.

00:46:03.860 --> 00:46:06.780 align:middle line:84%
And it may show my closed
mindedness on "Open Minds,"

00:46:06.780 --> 00:46:12.180 align:middle line:84%
but whatever that is, I always
had an immediate revulsion

00:46:12.180 --> 00:46:16.090 align:middle line:84%
at what I felt was really
asymmetrical-- like throwing

00:46:16.090 --> 00:46:17.950 align:middle line:90%
poo on a canvas.

00:46:17.950 --> 00:46:23.490 align:middle line:84%
And I'm supposed to evaluate
that and contemplate that.

00:46:23.490 --> 00:46:27.220 align:middle line:84%
I've not been able to do it,
because there is no beauty.

00:46:27.220 --> 00:46:30.160 align:middle line:84%
But that is how our world
has now been constructed.

00:46:30.160 --> 00:46:33.070 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: And I feel
very moved, and I

00:46:33.070 --> 00:46:37.990 align:middle line:84%
feel it's important to share
a story from Paracelsus'

00:46:37.990 --> 00:46:40.010 align:middle line:90%
time in the 1500s.

00:46:40.010 --> 00:46:45.210 align:middle line:84%
An individual had locked
themselves in a room,

00:46:45.210 --> 00:46:48.760 align:middle line:84%
closing all the windows,
closing all the doors,

00:46:48.760 --> 00:46:53.140 align:middle line:84%
and did not come out for
quite an amount of time.

00:46:53.140 --> 00:46:58.430 align:middle line:84%
And when they finally went
in, the individual was dead.

00:46:58.430 --> 00:47:00.680 align:middle line:84%
Now, there was
edicts during his era

00:47:00.680 --> 00:47:04.200 align:middle line:84%
that you have to close your
windows, at least at night,

00:47:04.200 --> 00:47:04.700 align:middle line:90%
or--

00:47:04.700 --> 00:47:06.700 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: The evil night
humors will get you.

00:47:06.700 --> 00:47:09.360 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: The devil will come
in or the plague will come in.

00:47:09.360 --> 00:47:12.470 align:middle line:84%
And they also said you take a
bath once a year, because you

00:47:12.470 --> 00:47:14.590 align:middle line:90%
don't want to hurt yourself.

00:47:14.590 --> 00:47:17.990 align:middle line:84%
When they went in there and
found this individual dead,

00:47:17.990 --> 00:47:22.780 align:middle line:84%
Paracelsus, unlike anyone
else who was there,

00:47:22.780 --> 00:47:25.450 align:middle line:84%
realized that there was
a great truth there.

00:47:25.450 --> 00:47:27.180 align:middle line:90%
What was the truth?

00:47:27.180 --> 00:47:30.200 align:middle line:84%
He recognized that
nothing from the outside

00:47:30.200 --> 00:47:32.680 align:middle line:84%
had killed this
individual, but something

00:47:32.680 --> 00:47:37.930 align:middle line:84%
within their own atmosphere
had poisoned them.

00:47:37.930 --> 00:47:42.160 align:middle line:84%
And so here was one
of his philosophies.

00:47:42.160 --> 00:47:46.840 align:middle line:84%
Anything that is
closed up and does not

00:47:46.840 --> 00:47:54.490 align:middle line:84%
have a fresh stream of energy or
knowledge will wither and die,

00:47:54.490 --> 00:48:01.450 align:middle line:84%
and that includes religions,
political parties,

00:48:01.450 --> 00:48:04.360 align:middle line:90%
individuals who are dogmatic.

00:48:04.360 --> 00:48:11.070 align:middle line:84%
That is an aspect of
nature, any closed system.

00:48:11.070 --> 00:48:14.390 align:middle line:84%
And this is where the old
hermetic philosophy comes in.

00:48:14.390 --> 00:48:16.090 align:middle line:90%
As above, so below.

00:48:16.090 --> 00:48:17.930 align:middle line:90%
And as below, so above.

00:48:17.930 --> 00:48:23.010 align:middle line:84%
There are fundamental truths
that reign through the cosmos.

00:48:23.010 --> 00:48:26.590 align:middle line:84%
These are some of the
hermetic philosophies that

00:48:26.590 --> 00:48:28.570 align:middle line:90%
have existed throughout time.

00:48:28.570 --> 00:48:31.300 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to bring
him up because that

00:48:31.300 --> 00:48:32.800 align:middle line:90%
is exactly what you're sharing.

00:48:32.800 --> 00:48:33.700 align:middle line:84%
