Our friend Paracelsus was at
a party that his parents had.

00:49:18.360 --> 00:49:19.820 align:middle line:90%
He was a young man.

00:49:19.820 --> 00:49:24.820 align:middle line:84%
And this sick dog
walked out of the party

00:49:24.820 --> 00:49:26.395 align:middle line:84%
and started to go
in the countryside.

00:49:26.395 --> 00:49:28.610 align:middle line:84%
And Paracelsus was very
young, and he said, well

00:49:28.610 --> 00:49:30.450 align:middle line:90%
I'd rather follow the dog.

00:49:30.450 --> 00:49:33.680 align:middle line:84%
And the dog who had been ill
walked into the countryside,

00:49:33.680 --> 00:49:37.260 align:middle line:84%
sniffing various
grasses and herbs.

00:49:37.260 --> 00:49:43.120 align:middle line:84%
Went on, and eventually started
eating an herb or a plant.

00:49:43.120 --> 00:49:44.340 align:middle line:90%
The dog lay down.

00:49:44.340 --> 00:49:50.610 align:middle line:84%
45 minutes later, it got up and
seemingly was perfectly normal.

00:49:50.610 --> 00:49:52.950 align:middle line:84%
And Paracelsus
wondered, why was it

00:49:52.950 --> 00:49:58.010 align:middle line:84%
that a dog could find out
what would work for him,

00:49:58.010 --> 00:49:59.700 align:middle line:90%
and as human beings--

00:49:59.700 --> 00:50:02.450 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Are looking to
someone above, below, whatever.

00:50:02.450 --> 00:50:03.890 align:middle line:84%
To the side, to
see our own truth.

00:50:03.890 --> 00:50:05.098 align:middle line:90%
